==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Marginal
<hw>Mar"gin*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>marginal</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of or pertaining to a
margin.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Written or printed in the margin; <as>as, a
<ex>marginal</ex> note or gloss</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>At the lower limit; barely sufficient; <as>as, of
<ex>marginal</ex> utility</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>marginal cost of production</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>marginal cost</ent>⟦br⟧
<mhw>
